about_the_game:
To commemorate Kou Shibusawa's 35th anniversary, the &quot;Kou Shibusawa Archives&quot; will be opened in the Steam Store. Here we will revive popular previously released titles.<br />
In this seventh round of releases, we offer the 1993 release of the first &quot;Winning Post.&quot; <br />
This game allows players to experience the romantic life of a horse owner. As an owner, you will interact with trainers, stable hands, and jockeys to raise the best racer you can. With a multiple of races of all ranks, both local and international, horses earn fame and renown until they win the chance to participate in the world's greatest race of all, the &quot;Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe.&quot;

